            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Vertices (1,1,1), (1,0,0), (0,1,0), (0,0,1). Rel vertices (0,-1,-1), (-1,0,-1), (-1,-1,0). Det = 1(1) + 1(-1) = 0? Wait. (0,-1,-1), (-1,0,-1), (-1,-1,0) -&gt; 0 - (-1)(-1) + (-1)(1) = -1 - 1 = -2. Volume = |-2|/6 = 1/3.</explanation></question>
